blog.title: Move Your Body
blog.description:
In a world where you can be anything; be kind.

29. Teacher. Married. Netballer. Gymer. Runner. Adventurer.

2 x half marathoner

5km PB - 25:25

10km PB - 52:01

summary:
Hello!
My dear friend and I conquered our half marathon yesterday and stuck to our goal! So proud. I shaved a few minutes off my...
body:
Hello!

My dear friend and I conquered our half marathon yesterday and stuck to our goal! So proud. I shaved a few minutes off my PB but even if I didn’t I would say it was a much more enjoyable run than my first half marathon. I had no cramping and I wasn’t shuffling along in agony like when I hit the wall last year. We stuck to our pace the whole way and although my flexors and calves did progressively tighten up I was able to keep going. I’m so proud of my friend for running her first half after only taking up running 14 months ago!!!

What a weekend 😍😍😍
